            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-low heat and add the<strong> cooked linguine</strong>, <strong>courgetti </strong>and <strong>crispy lardons</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>creamy bean sauce </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give it a good mix up until everything is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>'creamy' bacon & mushroom linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if it looks a little thick</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
